Majota Kambule, known as Phat Joe, has been trending at number one on Wednesday following comments he made on radio about Anele Mdoda being announced as the Miss SA 2019 judge. While he trended because of the comments, others opted to check out his previous tweets and likes, and some of those who did concluded that he may have been hacked.
If Twitter likes are anything to go by, the radio personality appears to be a huge fan of porn, and social media users find it hilarious.
